title: Stunning Modern Detached Home
description: Stunning 4-bedroom detached home in the heart of Toronto. This modern masterpiece features an open-concept living space, gourmet kitchen with premium appliances, and a beautifully landscaped backyard perfect for entertaining. Minutes from transit, shopping, and top-rated schools.

title: Luxury Waterfront Condo
description: Experience luxury living at its finest in this stunning waterfront condo with breathtaking lake views. Floor-to-ceiling windows, premium finishes throughout, and access to world-class amenities including pool, gym, and 24-hour concierge.

title: Charming Semi-Detached in Leslieville
description: Beautifully renovated semi-detached home in trendy Leslieville. Features include exposed brick, hardwood floors throughout, updated kitchen with quartz counters, and a private backyard oasis. Steps to Queen St shops, cafes, and restaurants.

title: Spacious Family Townhouse
description: Perfect family home! This spacious townhouse offers 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a finished basement. Modern open floor plan with gourmet kitchen, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. Private backyard and 2-car garage.

title: Executive Detached Home
description: Magnificent executive home in prestigious Oakville neighborhood. This stunning property features 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, grand foyer with soaring ceilings, chef's kitchen, home theatre, and resort-style backyard with pool and cabana.

title: Modern Downtown Condo
description: Sleek and modern 1-bedroom condo in the heart of downtown Toronto. Features floor-to-ceiling windows with stunning CN Tower views, upgraded kitchen, in-suite laundry, and access to premium building amenities. Perfect for young professionals.

title: Renovated Victorian Semi
description: Meticulously renovated Victorian semi in the vibrant Ossington neighborhood. Original charm meets modern luxury with exposed brick, custom millwork, designer kitchen, and spa-like ensuite. Rooftop terrace with city views.

title: Family Home with Pool
description: Beautiful family home featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a stunning inground pool. Updated kitchen with breakfast bar, formal dining room, finished basement with recreation room. Large lot with mature trees and privacy.

title: Boutique Loft Condo
description: Unique boutique loft in converted heritage building in the St. Lawrence Market area. Soaring 14-foot ceilings, exposed brick and ductwork, open-concept living space. Walking distance to shops, restaurants, and the waterfront.

title: Corner Unit Townhouse
description: Desirable corner unit townhouse with lots of natural light. Features include updated kitchen with stainless appliances, hardwood floors on main level, finished basement, and private fenced yard. Close to parks and schools.

title: Penthouse Suite with Terrace
description: Spectacular penthouse with massive wraparound terrace offering panoramic city views. Premium finishes throughout including marble floors, custom cabinetry, and chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances. The ultimate in urban luxury living.

title: Cozy Starter Home
description: Perfect starter home or investment property! This well-maintained semi-detached home features 2 bedrooms, updated bathroom, new roof, and a spacious backyard. Close to transit, Square One, and all amenities.
